Employees page is visible by the site Admin and Managers of Employees and Owners.
Site admin can view all employees by swithing in between companies they are assigned in the dropdown filter.
Managers can see all the employees asigned to the same company they are.
Owners can view employees by providing company from the dropdown filter. Owner can have only options of the companies they are assigned but system admin can see all companies.

Employee table
Full name
Email
Employee number
Department
Possition
Status
Managers (with tooltip to show all the options)
Managees (with tooltip to show all the options)
Actions (Deactivate and Manage relations)